Package oop.quizzler.controller

Class InitQuizzler

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
oop.quizzler.controller.InitQuizzler
public class InitQuizzler extends javafx.application.Application
Class used as a starting and turning point for the application. Importent for the communication and change between the different views. Contains helper methods and objects for the controllers.
